                    <span>I found this book to be not that good. It is a bit long winded, I had a hard time using the index to find things that I was looking for. It helped me get a bit more expertise but didn't help me get to a very good level of expertise. I rarely use this book now, I would recommend looking else where for a better book to both learn and use as a reference. Wrong first buy or only buy.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Learning to use one of the best editors!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
